Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.06,0:00:05.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Come get your delicious okonomiyaki!}Hãy thử món Okonomiyaki ngon tuyệt này!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:07.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Oops, excuse m-}A, xin lỗ--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.77,0:00:14.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{A-Akuma is walking with a girl?!}A-Akuma đi cùng một cô gái?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.48,0:00:16.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{She's wearing our junior high section's uniform!}Mặc đồng phục cấp 2 kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.31,0:00:17.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Is this a kidnapping?!}Bắt cóc à?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:21.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Everyone's staring daggers at me!}Mọi người đang nhìn mình!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.06,0:00:23.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Forgive me...}Xin lỗi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.02,0:00:25.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{At times like this... I should smile...}Lúc này cần phải nở nụ cười...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.56,0:00:28.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Didn't mean to scare you to DEATH...}Tao ổn lắm...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.64,0:00:31.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Death?! H-h-help!}Ổn? C-Cứu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:33.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{DEATH? N-no! I said I scared you to death!}À ý tôi không phải là thế!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:35.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{D-d-d-don't kill me!}Đ-Đừng giết tôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.93,0:00:36.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Big Brother.}Anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.23,0:00:39.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{What are you even doing?}Anh làm gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.14,0:00:41.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I wish you'd escort me properly.}Phải hộ tống em đàng hoàng chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:42.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{O-okay.}À ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.35,0:00:45.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{It's more crowded than I imagined!}Đông hơn mình nghĩ.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.77,0:00:48.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Val love "Campus Festival Date"...}Val Love "Hẹn hò tại lễ hội trường"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.10,0:00:49.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Seems like it's a bonus stage}Có vẻ là một nhiệm vụ bonus
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.73,0:00:53.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{where the more we go around together\Nthe more experience points we acquire,}nếu chúng ta đi cùng nhau càng nhiều thì sẽ càng tăng điểm kinh nghiệm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.14,0:00:55.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{but I have to make sure I do my best\Nnot to die from fear!}Nhưng mình phải chuẩn bị tinh thần để không chết vì sợ!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.06,0:00:57.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Big Brother.}Anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.10,0:01:00.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I wish you'd hurry up.}Nhanh lên.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.98,0:01:05.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{You two sure took your time!}Hai người đến trễ vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.10,0:01:08.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{But what's wrong?\NYou look like you're about to die.}Sao thế? Mặt cậu như sắp chết vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.43,0:01:11.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{N-nothing. It's very crowded.}K-Không có gì, hơi đông thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.23,0:01:12.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I'm hungry...}Em đói...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.73,0:01:15.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I'll take you to a table, so hold on a second.}Để chị dẫn đến bàn, chờ chút.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.68,0:01:17.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Please take your time and enjoy!}Hãy từ từ chọn món.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.23,0:01:18.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Th-thanks.}C-cảm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:20.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{What is it?}Đây là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.89,0:01:23.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I-It's nyaathing!}K-Không có gì nyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.93,0:01:27.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Something weird's going on with Natsuki-san.}Natsuki có gì đó kì lạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.14,0:01:29.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Did I do something wrong again?}Mình lại làm gì sai à?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.52,0:01:31.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{But right now...}Nhưng bây giờ...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.10,0:01:32.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{What?}Cái gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.31,0:01:34.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Er, nothing!}À không.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.93,0:01:38.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Uh, Yakumo-san, what would you like to eat?}Yakumo, em muốn ăn gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.23,0:01:41.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Anything is fine,\Nso I wish you'd hurry up and choose.}Gì cũng được, nên anh chọn nhanh lên.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.31,0:01:43.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I-I-I'm sorry!}X-X-Xin lỗi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.93,0:01:47.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I'm getting agitated for some reason.}Sao tự nhiên mình lại ghen nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.35,0:01:49.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Okay, this is where I...}Rồi, mình sẽ...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.27,0:01:53.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Let's see... well then, we'll have this\Nsquid ink pasta with squid ink on the side...}Xem nào... Pasta mực với mực của con mực...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.98,0:01:55.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Sorry for the wait!}Xin lỗi vì đã chờ!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:57.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Here's the Lovey-Dovey Couple drink!}Đây là nước uống cặp đôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:01:59.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Um... err...}À ừm...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:03.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{It's alright, this is my treat. After all, I'm...}Không sao, tôi đãi. Vì tôi là...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:05.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Yakumo's big sister, you know!}Chị gái của Yakumo mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:07.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{O-okay, I appreciate your kindness.}À ừm, vậy cảm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:09.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Ew.}Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.39,0:02:10.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:13.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I don't wanna drink from the same cup as you.}Em không muốn uống cùng ly với anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:14.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{That's gross.}Kinh tởm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:15.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{But...}N-Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.81,0:02:18.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{If you insist, though...}Nếu anh muốn đến thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.93,0:02:22.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Then suck on this.}Thì liếm nó đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.48,0:02:25.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{May as well since we'll be\Ndrinking it together, right?}Dù gì cũng là uống chung mà nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:27.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Uh, but...}À ừm, nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.14,0:02:28.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I wish you'd get on with it.}Em muốn anh liếm nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.98,0:02:31.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{R-right! Sorry.}P-Phải nhỉ! Xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.35,0:02:43.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{You're so bad at this... easy with the teeth.}Anh cắn chặt quá... Thả lỏng răng ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:45.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{S-s-sorry.}X-X-Xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:47.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Sue is so much better at this.}Sue còn làm tốt hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:53.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{That feels nice.}Nhưng cũng không tệ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.85,0:02:55.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Do you want to drink more?}Muốn nữa không?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:57.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{U-uh, yes, please.}À ừm, muốn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.81,0:03:00.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{My neck is getting stiff.}Cổ mình đang bị cứng...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.64,0:03:02.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I'll adjust my posture...}Chỉnh lại tư thế đã...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.02,0:03:06.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Woah, I'm soaked. Gross.}A, ướt nhẹp rồi. Kinh quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.06,0:03:09.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{S-s-s-sorry!}X-X-Xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.31,0:03:13.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Were you hoping to suck on something like this too?}Anh muốn làm việc đó tại đây luôn à?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:16.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Pervert.}Biến thái.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:17.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Stab!}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.18,0:03:19.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Yakumo! You can't take your clothes off here!}Yakumo! Em không thể lột đồ ở đây được!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:21.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Natsuki, get off my back.}Natsuki, quay mặt lại đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:23.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,M-Mặc quần áo vào ngay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:26.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Ooh, there's a huge crowd here.}Đông đúc quá nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:28.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{But what are you guys doing?}Mà mấy đứa đang làm gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:31.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Misa, sisters, hey there!}Chào mấy chị!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:33.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Getting here was pretty rough.}Đến được đây khó lắm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:35.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Pretty rough!}Khó lắm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.35,0:03:38.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Everyone seems to be fully\Nenjoying themselves despite that.}Nhưng em trông mọi người có vẻ vui vẻ lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.39,0:03:40.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Hey, what the hell is going on there?}C-Chuyện này là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:42.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Tên Ác quỷ đang được gái bu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:44.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{This absolutely has to be...}Không thể nhầm được...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:46.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Blackmail!}Sự đe dọa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:50.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{My stomach hurts!}Đau bụng quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:52.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{By the way, Takuma-chan.}Mà nè Takuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:55.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Are you okay with being Natsuki-chan's\Npartner for the dance party?}Để Natsuki nhảy cùng ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:58.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Y-you mean that thing?}C-Chuyện đó ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:04:00.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{What are you talking about?}Chuyện gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:03.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I heard there's a late-night festival where\Na man and a woman pair up and dance.}Nghe nói rằng trường có tổ chức buổi nhảy múa nam nữ vào buổi tối.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:05.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Is there a huge event like that?!}Có sự kiện đó sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.73,0:04:08.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{D-dance party, huh?}T-Tiệc nhảy à?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:11.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{But I have no interest whatsoever\Nin cute things like that!}Nhưng em không có hứng thú mấy chuyện đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:15.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{And I've never thought anything like\NI'd like to try dancing with Takuma at least once...}Và cũng chưa từng nghĩ sẽ nhảy cùng Takuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:16.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{You're so obvious!}Dễ hiểu quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:19.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I think Natsuki would make a good partner.}Chị nghĩ Natsuki ổn mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:22.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I sincerely do not care.}Em thì sao cũng được.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:23.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{R-really?}T-Thật hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:26.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{But I want to dance too!}Nhưng em cũng muốn nhảy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:28.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Which do you like more, dancing or snacks?}Em thích nhảy hay ăn bánh hơn?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:29.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Snacks!}Ăn bánh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:35.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{W-well, I don't care either way,\Nbut if that's what everyone wants...}V-Vậy thì em sao cũng được, nếu mọi người năn nỉ đến vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.43,0:04:37.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Er, well, you see....}À nhưng mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.18,0:04:39.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{It's just that I don't want to go with Natsuki,}Em không muốn nhảy với Natsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:44.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{but lately people have been getting scarier to me\Nday by day or something like that,}Gần đây mọi người tự nhiên đáng sợ hơn với mình,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:50.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{and it feels even more like I'm gonna get killed\Nif I'm with such a popular girl like Natsuki-san.}và cảm giác như tôi sẽ bị cậu giết nếu nhảy cùng...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:54.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{So maybe it'd be better\Nif I paired up with someone else...}Nên là tôi sẽ tìm người khác...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:57.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Er, um...}À thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:05:00.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I forgot that I'm working right now.}Tôi quên mình còn phải làm việc.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:02.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Big Sisters, see you later!}Gặp chị sau nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.27,0:05:07.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Takumacchi, pretend that\Nfairly awful exchange didn't happen.}Takumacchi... Em vừa làm một chuyện độc ác đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.14,0:05:08.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Huh?!}Hả?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:09.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Yes, that was fairly awful.}Phải, thật khủng khiếp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.23,0:05:11.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{A fairy?}Khủng khiếp gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:14.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Nanna the Fairy always\Ngives me snacks so I love Nanna!}Nếu là có bánh kẹo thì Nanna thích lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:20.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I just don't want to go with Natsuki-san.}Tôi không muốn nhảy với Natsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:24.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I get that he has no interest in me, but...}Mình biết hắn không có hứng thú với mình, nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:26.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Natsuki-chan, are you okay?}Natsuki, em ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.31,0:05:29.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I thought you might be feeling down.}Chị nghĩ chắc đang thất vọng lắm hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.23,0:05:31.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{N-No, I'm not.}L-Làm gì có.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:33.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Still so young...}Vẫn còn trẻ con lắm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:37.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{M-more importantly, Big Sister Futaba,\Nare you all doing okay?}Q-Quan trọng hơn, bên chị Futaba vẫn ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:40.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I'm shocked everyone came today, too.}Chị cũng sốc khi vừa mới đến đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:43.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Goodness, what a day this has turned into...}Không ngờ chuyện này lại xảy ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.06,0:05:44.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{What is this?!}Cái gì đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.48,0:05:46.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I'm looking forward to seeing who wins.}Chị đang mong chờ xem ai thắng đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:48.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I didn't enter this!}Em không tham gia đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:49.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Someone else chose to do that!}Ai lại tự tiện đăng kí vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:51.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Itsuyo-chan applied to this!}Itsuyo đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.77,0:05:53.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{She said it was a competition.}Con bé bảo là cuộc thi đấu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:54.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{That idiot!}Con ngốc đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:57.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{But there's something else I really want to hear about!}Nhưng đây không phải chuyện em muốn hỏi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.56,0:05:58.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I already know.}Chị biết rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.93,0:06:02.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Big Sister Ichika is on alert for us.}Chị Ichika đang cảnh giác cho chúng ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.85,0:06:04.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{The captain is?!}Đội trưởng á?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:08.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{The campus festival is a chance for\Nall of us to raise our levels at once.}Lễ hội trường là cơ hội tất cả cùng tăng cấp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.81,0:06:11.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{But the buildings are now densely packed.}Nhưng mật độ các tòa nhà đang rất dày đặc.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.06,0:06:13.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Therefore, the crowd is overflowing.}Và đám đông cũng quá tải.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:17.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Under these circumstances,\Nthe enemy is definitely setting something up.}Chắc chắn kẻ thù đang có âm mưu gì đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:23.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Three guests, coming through.}Ba vị khách.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:26.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{A-Akuma?! Someone come work the front for me!}A-Ác quỷ?! Ai đó thay tôi ca này!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:32.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{This is pretty professional.}Chuyên nghiệp nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:34.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Uh, Takuma?!}Takuma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:38.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I don't mind ghosts, but when I think about\Npeople dressing up I-I-I-I...}Em không sợ ma quỷ nhưng người mặc nó thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:40.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Your phobia of people!}Em sợ người à?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:41.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{And what's wrong with you, Kururi?!}Còn Kururi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:43.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I thought it was a snack house!}Em tưởng đây là nhà bánh kẹo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:45.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{That's not even close!}Khác nhau hoàn toàn mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.35,0:06:46.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Misa-san...}Chị Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:47.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Big Sis Misa...}Chị Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:50.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{You two are hopeless. Jeez.}Hai em đúng là...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:53.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Watch your step, okay?}Cẩn thận bước chân.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:56.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Sorry, Big Sister Misa.}Xin lỗi chị Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:59.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I-I-I'm truly sorry about this...}E-E-Em thực sự xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:03.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{You know, Takuma, a guy\Nreally shouldn't cower that much.}Mà này Takuma, là đàn ông đừng có nhát gan nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.85,0:07:05.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{It lowers your self-worth.}Nó chỉ hạ thấp giá trị của em thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:07.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Huh? Oh well... Er...}Hả? À vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:09.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I-I'm sorry.}Em xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:10.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{You said it again.}Lại nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.10,0:07:11.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I-I-I'm sorry!}X-X-Xin lỗi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.43,0:07:12.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Listen to me.}Nghe này.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:16.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{When you're feeling helpless,\Ndon't say "sorry," say "Thanks."}Khi em cảm thấy vô vọng thì đừng xin lỗi mà hãy nói cảm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:19.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{That sounds way cooler.}Như thế ngầu hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:20.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Misa-san...}Chị Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:21.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Maybe it's because her hair is nice and neat,}Có thể vì tóc chị ấy hôm nay gọn gàng và đẹp lạ thường...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:22.85,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,{Maybe it's because her hair is nice and neat,}Có thể vì tóc chị ấy hôm nay gọn gàng và đẹp lạ thường...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:23.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Maybe it's because her hair is nice and neat,}Có thể vì tóc chị ấy hôm nay gọn gàng và đẹp lạ thường...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:25.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{but she seems less aggressive than usual.}Nhưng hình như tính cách cũng tích cực hơn thì phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:27.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Thank you, Big Sister Misa.}Cảm ơn chị Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:29.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{You're welcome.}Không có gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:32.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Th-that stupid Akuma!}T-Tên Ác quỷ khốn kiếp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.35,0:07:37.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{While I'm covered in sweat from working\Nhe's freakin' flirting with girls!}Khi mình đang chảy mồ hôi ở đây thì nó đi đu đưa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.23,0:07:40.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Maybe it's time to settle old scores, huh?!}Đã đến lúc giải quyết thù cũ rồi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:43.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Also, apologize to Natsuki later, okay?}Và tí nữa nhớ xin lỗi Natsuki nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:46.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{All of that made her pretty angry.}Chuyện đó làm con bé giận lắm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.06,0:07:49.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Er, why was Natsuki-san angry?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.77,0:07:51.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{You should at least figure that part out on your own...}Ít nhất thì em cũng tự tìm hiểu đi chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.14,0:07:55.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{R-right, er... Sorry.}V-Vâng... Xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:58.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Or maybe I should say "thanks"?}Hay là cảm ơn nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.89,0:08:01.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{You're very rigid, aren't you?}Em cứng nhắc quá đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:03.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{That's another reason Natsuki is angry with you!}Đó là lý do cũng khiến Natsuki giận đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.31,0:08:05.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I-I'm sorry.}E-Em xin lỗi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.31,0:08:11.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Kururi?! What's wrong with her?}Kururi? Sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.43,0:08:12.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Who knows.}Ai biết...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.89,0:08:16.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Of course you'd be afraid of a live eel.}Dĩ nhiên phải sợ lươn sống rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:18.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Now for the other two.}Giờ thì hai đứa còn lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:27.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Wh-what happened?!}S-Sao vậy ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:29.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{There's something in my clothes!}Có gì đó trong quần áo chị!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:30.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,T-Takuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.43,0:08:31.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Yes?}Vâng?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.27,0:08:35.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I can't stand... the wriggling...}Chị không thể,,, chịu nổi mấy thứ nhớp nháp...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:38.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Get it out...}Lấy nó ra đi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:41.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{O-okay. Here goes...}E-Em hiểu rồi, vậy thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:47.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{N-no, go lower!}Không, thấp hơn nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.68,0:08:51.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I-I'm sorry, I mean, thank you very much!}X-Xin lỗi, à không, cảm ơn rất nhiều!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:53.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{You idiot!}Thằng ngốc!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.23,0:09:04.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{No... don't touch me there!}Không... đừng chạm vào chỗ đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:11.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I'll let it go outside!}Em sẽ ra ngoài!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.56,0:09:13.10,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,{Hey, someone might be falling out of the window!}Này, có ai té từ cửa sổ nữa kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:15.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I-idiot... Now he's alone...\NHey, someone might be falling out of the window!}N-Ngốc... Đừng có bỏ chị lại chứ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.10,0:09:16.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I-idiot... Now he's alone...\NHey, someone might be falling out of the window!}N-Ngốc... Đừng có bỏ chị lại chứ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:17.64,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,{Is he falling or not?}Té chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:19.27,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,{He fell!}Rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:24.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I-I'm exhausted.}M-Mệt quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:27.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{What am I doing?}Mình đang làm trò gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:32.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I was planning to focus on my studies\Nduring the campus festival...}Đáng ra phải tập trung học hành chứ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:35.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Seriously, why in the world is this happening?}Tại sao chuyện này lại xảy ra?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:36.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Akutsu-senpai?}Anh Akutsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:39.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Uh, y-you're from the student council...}E-Em là bên Hội học sinh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:43.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I'm Inukai. What are you doing here?}Em là Inukai, anh làm gì ở đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:48.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Huh?! W-Well to be honest,\NI thought this eel here was a ghost,}À thì... Anh thấy một con lươn trong nhà ma,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:51.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{and uh, I went out to look for some water I guess, um...}nên là đang đi tìm chỗ thả nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:54.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{You're very entertaining.}Câu chuyện thú vị nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:58.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{He's the first person I've talked to\Nbesides Natsuki-san and her sisters,}Cậu ấy là người đầu tiên nói chuyện bình thường với mình ngoài mấy chị em.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:10:01.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{but I'm doing fairly well... kind of...}Mình vẫn làm khá tốt nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:06.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{But I'm shocked to see that you're\Nactually enjoying the festival, Senpai.}Nhưng em sốc khi thấy anh đang tận hưởng lễ hội đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.85,0:10:10.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Actually... I, uh... was invited by someone I know.}Thực ra... anh được mời đến...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:13.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{O-oh, is that so?}T-Thế à?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.10,0:10:17.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Then I suppose I have to show some appreciation\Nto that person you know, right?}Vậy thì em phải thể hiện để không phụ lòng sự đánh giá của anh mới được.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.23,0:10:20.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Where did Takuma-san go?}Takuma chạy đâu rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.48,0:10:22.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{He might be over here.}Chắc bên kia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:24.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{What, are you feeling discouraged, Natsuki?!}Sao tự nhiên nản chí vậy, Natsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:26.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Huh? I-I'm really not...}Hả? L-Làm gì có...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:30.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I do think that it'll be fine since\NBig Sister Ichika is here, but...}Biết là chị Ichika đang ở đây nhưng mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.43,0:10:35.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Excuse us, we're in a hurry. Let us pass through here.}Xin lỗi, xin để bọn tôi qua...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.31,0:10:41.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I've been worried about you this whole time.}Em đã luôn lo cho anh suốt đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.31,0:10:44.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I had no idea what I'd do if you hadn't shown up.}Mãi mà anh vẫn chưa thể hiện gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.93,0:10:47.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I thought I would starve to death...}Cảm giác sắp chết đói vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:10:57.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{An akuma!}Ác quỷ!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.81,0:11:06.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Those akuma are the kind that possess humans!}Chúng là đám ác quỷ hôm trước!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.98,0:11:10.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Did they really possess the entire academy?!}Chúng đã xâm chiếm toàn học viện sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:16.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Someone once said that love is\Nthe source of a maiden's power.}Ai đó đã từng nói tình yêu là ngọn nguồn của sức mạnh thiếu nữ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.06,0:11:20.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{That's why I must stop that source.}Thế nên cần phải ngăn cản sức mạnh đó lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.77,0:11:27.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Battling maidens without their Einheijer\Nare the same as pigs that only exist to be eaten.}Chiến đấu với đám thiếu nữ mà không có\N Einheijer cũng như mổ lợn để ăn thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:31.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Now then...}Giờ thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.14,0:11:34.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Here's the main dish I've been waiting for.}Đây là món chính ta đã mong chờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.31,0:11:41.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Quả nhiên kẻ địch đã làm gì đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.14,0:11:42.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Big Sister Misa!}Chị Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:45.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Take a look at this. It's the entrance to the barrier.}Nhìn xem. Là lối vào cổng kết giới.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:48.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Did Big Brother put the akuma inside a barrier?}Anh trai đã đưa ác quỷ vào trong đó ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:52.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{The barrier manifestation point is\Nthe little finger of Einheijer's left hand.}Điểm khai mở kết giới là ngón tay út bên trái của Einheijer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:56.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Th-then where in the world is Takuma?}V-Vậy của Takuma ở đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:11:59.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Could it be that after the barrier was stretched,\Nhe fell victim to the enemy?}Không lẽ kẻ địch đã bẫy cậu ấy vào kết giới?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.23,0:12:03.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{It's because we left him on his own!}Là vì chúng ta đã bỏ cậu ấy lại...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:05.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{There's no point talking about\Nwhat what's already done.}Chuyện đã rồi cũng chẳng làm được gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:08.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{For now, we need to do something about that akuma.}Đầu tiên cần làm gì đó đám ác quỷ kia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.14,0:12:12.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{At this rate the barrier will be broken\Nand Midgard will perish!}Cứ thế này thì kết giới bị phá hủy và Midgard sẽ diệt vong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:14.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{There are two ways to destroy the barrier.}Có hai cách để phá hủy kết giới.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:18.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{We can either destroy it from the inside,\Nor destroy it from the entrance on the outside.}Phá từ bên trong hoặc bên ngoài.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.89,0:12:21.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Natsuki, stand by in front of the entrance.}Natsuki, chờ ở lối vào.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.27,0:12:23.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I need you to guard the outside.}Chị cần em canh cổng.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:25.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{G-got it.}E-Em hiểu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.48,0:12:27.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{But what about you and everyone else?}Nhưng còn chị và mọi người?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:29.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Until Takuma gets here,}Đến khi gặp được Takuma,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:34.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{we'll go inside and keep that akuma in check!}bọn chị sẽ vào kết giới và tiêu diệt con ác quỷ đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:37.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{It sure is huge now that I'm seeing it up close.}Đứng gần mới thấy nó to quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.64,0:12:40.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I-I wonder if we'll get out of this alive...}K-Không biết có sống nổi không...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:43.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{We're not necessarily trying to defeat it.}Chúng ta không cần hạ nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.77,0:12:46.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Remember what our teacher told us?}Nhớ lời sư phụ dạy không?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.06,0:12:49.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{When up against a stronger enemy,\Nthe three guidelines are:}Khi gặp kẻ địch mạnh, có 3 nguyên tắc:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:51.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{"Don't worry about your weaknesses."}"Đừng lo lắng về điểm yếu của mình".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:53.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{"Don't rush in without a plan."}"Đừng tấn công mà không có kế hoạch".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:55.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{"Don't die."}"Đừng chết".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.43,0:12:57.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Surviving means you can\Nhave a meal with everyone again.}Sống sót là em có thể được ăn uống cùng mọi người một bữa nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.93,0:13:00.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{That's not something you need to point out to us!}C-Chị không cần nói em cũng biết!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:02.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I see. Sorry about that.}Vậy à, xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.35,0:13:05.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Well then, are you two ready?}Còn hai đứa đã chuẩn bị chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:07.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Sacred Sword "Cannon," strengthened.}Thánh kiếm "Cannon", cường hóa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.02,0:13:10.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Kururi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:11.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nhận lấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:19.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Keep them apart and don't let their awareness\Nturn towards the barrier.}Giữa chúng ở xa và đừng để tiếp cận kết giới!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:20.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Got it!}Rõ!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:29.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{There are so many of them!}Nhiều quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:34.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Disgraceful!}Cút!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:36.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Oh no...}Chết...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:44.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{C-Captain!}Đ-Đội trưởng...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.14,0:13:46.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Sorry I'm late.}Xin lỗi, chị đến muộn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.14,0:13:48.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I-it's okay, you saved us!}K-Không sao, chị đã cứu em.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.73,0:13:50.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I received a message from Misa.}Chị đã nhận tin từ Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:54.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{She said there's a possibility that weakling\Ngot captured by the enemy.}Em ấy nói rằng tên yếu đuối kia đã bị địch bắt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:56.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Well...}Chuyện đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:59.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{So this is what happens when you're\Naway from him for even a few moments... Pitiful.}Chỉ vừa rời mắt một chút mà hắn đã bị bắt à? Thật thảm hại.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:02.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I'm pissed we have to deal with\Nthe consequences of his failures,}Thật bực mình khi phải đối phó với thất bại của hắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:04.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{but we'll protect the barrier until the end!}Nhưng chúng ta sẽ bảo vệ kết giới đến khi kết thúc.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:06.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{R-right!}R-Rõ!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.85,0:14:10.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Takuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:12.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{please be safe!}hãy bình an.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:21.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Y-yummy! Tasty, tasty, this meal is so tasty!}Ngon quá! Quá ngon, ngon quá đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:26.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Those piggies are going to meet their end\Nwithout me even laying a finger on them.}Lũ heo đó sẽ tự kết thúc mọi chuyện mà chẳng cần chúng ta ra tay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:29.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{The meal I'm having while watching all of this go down...}Trong khi ngồi đây tận hưởng bữa ăn ngon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.31,0:14:36.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{It's all so scrumptious!}Quá tuyệt vời!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:41.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Don't you agree, Akutsu-senpai?}Anh cũng nghĩ thế chứ, Akutsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:43.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{What do you think?}Anh nghĩ sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.43,0:14:45.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{How do you like this banquet I'm hosting?}Có thích bữa tiệc này không?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.35,0:14:48.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Have yourself a bite too, Senpai!}Anh cũng ăn đi chứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.85,0:14:50.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Here, come on!}Nào nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:55.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Get to eating, already!}Ăn đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:15:01.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{How dare you act so ungrateful\Ntowards me for sparing your life? Eh?!}Sao mày dám thất lễ với tao chỉ vì vết đâm đó chứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.39,0:15:06.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Well, that's fine. The banquet has just started.}Kệ đi, bữa tiệc chỉ mới mở màn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.68,0:15:10.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Let's take our time and enjoy ourselves...}Hãy từ từ tận hưởng nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:15.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Let's watch those piggies get sloppily devoured...}Xem lũ heo đó bị ăn thịt từ từ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.18,0:15:23.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I have five string puppets left...}Chỉ còn 5 con búp bê...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:25.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Chịu nổi không đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.35,0:15:28.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Oh no, Itsuyo! That's...}Đồ ngốc! Itsuyo, bên đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.27,0:15:36.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Oh no!}Chết!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:40.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{My body... No!}Cơ thể mình... Không...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:43.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Help me, Father...}Cứu con, cha ơi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:45.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Takuma-san!}Takuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:47.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Itsuyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:48.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Kururi-chan, wait!}Kururi, khoan đã!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:51.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Love is the source of power?}Tình yêu là ngọn nguồn sức mạnh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.52,0:15:53.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{You make me laugh.}Đừng có giỡn mặt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.52,0:15:57.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Having to rely on such a thing for power,\Nit is of no importance.}Phải dựa vào một thứ như vậy để có sức mạnh, thật vớ vẩn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:15:59.48,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,{Big Sister Mutsumi!\NPower is the rampaging appetite itself!}Chị Mutsumi!\N Sức mạnh là sự thèm ăn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.48,0:16:00.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sức mạnh là sự thèm ăn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:03.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{You two, stay back!}Hai đứa lùi lại!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:12.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Svadilfari sẽ tiêu thụ tất cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:14.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{He'll turn the bait into puppets,}Biến những con mồi của mình thành những con rối,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:16.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{and their pain, their pleasure,}và nỗi đau, niềm vui của chúng,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.77,0:16:19.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{their souls will all be eaten up.}linh hồn của chúng sẽ bị nuốt trọn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.60,0:16:21.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{He's already sunk his fangs in...}Nó đã giương nanh vuốt ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.27,0:16:26.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Giờ chỉ còn thưởng thức thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:32.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{What's keeping the barrier up\Nis the fact that the weakling is still alive.}Kết giới vẫn còn tức là tên đó vẫn đang sống.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.23,0:16:35.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I presume that means the enemy has not killed him.}Có vẻ kẻ thù đã không giết hắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:37.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{What does that mean?}Vậy là sao ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:40.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I'm not sure why, but one thing that's clear is}Chị không rõ lý do nhưng
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:45.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{unless the weakling escapes from\Nthe hand of the enemy, it's over for us.}nếu tên yếu đuối đó không trốn thoát thì chúng ta cũng xong đời.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:48.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I believe in him.}Em tin vào cậu ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:52.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Because Takuma-kun is our lover!}Vì Takuma là người tình của chúng ta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:56.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I can't move my body.}Không thể di chuyển cơ thể...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:16:59.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Maybe that's because there's a hole in my stomach}Có thể là do bụng mình có cái lỗ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.52,0:17:02.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I wonder what happened to everyone else.}Mọi người sao rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:08.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{No... My mind is so foggy...}Không ổn... Tâm trí mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.35,0:17:16.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Sorry, Mom. I couldn't keep my promise.}Xin lỗi mẹ, con không thể giữ lời...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:19.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry, everyone...}Xin lỗi mọi người...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:31.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{E-excuse me.}X-Xin thứ lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.64,0:17:35.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{What do you want? Today's the festival, you know?}Có chuyện gì? Hôm nay là lễ hội đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:37.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{You know we have to practice for the dance.}Cậu biết chúng ta phải tập nhảy cùng nhau mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:38.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Dance?}Nhảy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:40.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I-it's nyaathing!}K-Không có gì nyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:46.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Uh, a-actually, I was thinking I wasn't\Na suitable lover after all...}T-Thực ra tôi đang nghĩ mình không phù hợp để làm người yêu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.18,0:17:49.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{So... I'm very sorry...}Nên là... xin lỗi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:53.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{And there's no way I can accept this.}Và chắc là cậu sẽ không nhận thứ này...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.56,0:17:55.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{What? Why?}Cái gì? Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:18:01.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I heard from Misa-san that it was highly likely\Nan enemy would attack during the festival.}Nghe chị Misa nói có khả năng cao kẻ thù sẽ tấn công trong ngày lễ hội.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:06.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{In other words, you want to run away\Nbecause you don't want to put yourself in danger.}Tóm lại cậu muốn bỏ chạy vì không muốn bản thân gặp nguy hiểm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:07.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Is that what you're saying?!}Muốn nói vậy chứ gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:09.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Yes, that's right.}Phải...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:15.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{I mean, if I die no one will be able to\Ntransform anymore, right?}Vì nếu tôi chết thì mọi người sẽ không thể biến hình được.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.23,0:18:20.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{My legs won't stop shaking, even now.}Chân tôi lúc này cũng đang run rẩy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:25.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{The way that I am now,\NI can't do anything when I need to.}Đó chính là tôi, chẳng thể làm gì khi thời khắc đến.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:30.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Leave me behind with everyone who can't fight\Nand I'll die in an instant!}Chỉ làm cản trở mọi người và sẽ chết ngay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:32.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{That's why, well...}Thế nên là...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:34.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{So you really are...}Cậu đúng là...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:35.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{an idiot.}đồ ngốc.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:36.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{Huh?!}HẢ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.73,0:18:39.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{You being incompetent isn't anything new,}Cái việc cậu kém cỏi ai chẳng biết,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:43.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{and absolutely no one here expects you\Nto suddenly spring into action now!}và cũng chẳng ai kì vọng cậu sẽ biến thành anh hùng đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.77,0:18:48.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{If you're always assuming that you're going to die\Nthen there's nothing to be done about that.}Mà cậu thì lúc nào chả lo lắng mình sẽ chết.
